jobs.description:
To ensure that the profile data fetched from the API is correctly populated into the form inputs, you'll need to update the form with the fetched data once it's available. This involves setting the default values of the form inputs using the reset method from react-hook-form after fetching the profile data.

Here’s how you can adjust your ProfilePageComp component to accomplish this:

Update Form Values: Use the reset method from react-hook-form to populate the form with fetched profile data.

Handle File Inputs: Ensure that the file input is managed correctly, particularly when updating or resetting it.
